Package: ClinicalValidators
Title: Clinical Calculation Validators - Reference Implementations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Timothy", "Hartzog", email = "timothy@hartzog.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reference implementations of pediatric and neonatal clinical calculations
    verified against peer-reviewed literature and official guidelines (AAP Red Book, CDC).
    Includes weight-based dosing, growth calculations, and severity scores.
    Cross-validated with Python and Julia implementations.
